{"tid":391962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報指撕掉「港獨」海報行為正義　值得讚好鼓勵","createTime":"2017-09-08T07:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T13:20:17.000Z","uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cdd28f954dc71592e567471eae4cc69a3d2f6f7","tid":391962,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T07:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1352956_1_20170908094032.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1352956_1_20170908094032.jpg&h=883c07f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《人民日報海外版》一篇文章，談到本港近日有大學民主牆張貼「港獨」海報的事件。文章認為，「港獨」分子雖然不多，但「動作」不少，以學生會名義開展，便可以宣稱「代表了所有學生」。文章批評，近年學生會代表性很差，雖然標榜「自主」，實則幕後和社會上的「港獨」分子眉來眼去。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，有學生站出來撕掉他們的海報，在社交平台發起「拒絕被代表」的行動，這些自發自覺的正義之舉，值得讚好和鼓勵。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，社會有共識，學生有覺悟，校方應有力度，法律措施亦必須跟上。回歸二十周年之後，香港正決心聚焦發展經濟、改善民生，形勢向好，斷不能容忍「一粒老鼠屎壞了一鍋湯」。把握新一輪的發展機遇，社會需要祛邪「獨」已是當務之急。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1352956-20170908.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1352956-20170908.htm&d=hZxFouYXqEcKQXDZPuqUTDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=1ecd5215\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1352956-20170908.htm&h=ad43e02a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1352956-20170908.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a30c99e301b6d34f1ded34e5082b7f339a0cd0cd","tid":391962,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T07:28:35.000Z","msg":"文革來了"},{"pid":"8d716a56bd51960f8255b7c3cf972e6849754c83","tid":391962,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T07:30:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>文革來了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bc14564f4575195b1f273fb722c19aebdde88f","tid":391962,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0